➜橘子和橙子的区别
http://www.sohu.com/a/435580230_100171577	31287
<p>接下来给大家科普一下，橘子和橙子的区别</p>
<p><strong>橘子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又叫桔子，学名“宽皮桔”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长相扁圆, 皮很好剥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而橘子的正确英文表达有两个：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>① mandarin</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>② tangerine</strong></p>
<p>A <strong>mandarin</strong>is a small orange whose skin comes off easily.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">细心的宝宝们肯定发现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>mandarin的首字母大写时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>就表示“普通话”</strong></p>
<p><strong>ღ 例句 ღ</strong></p>
<p><strong>Do you prefer oranges or mandarins?</strong></p>
<p>你喜欢吃橘子还是橙子呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201201/af825d8b85f3493c988682cc0ce819bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>橙子 orange</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长相是饱满的圆形或者长圆形</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皮很难剥</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
