<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">性凉，清凉下火</p>
<p>An orangeis a round juicy fruit with a thick, orange coloured skin，which is very hard to peel.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>ღ 例句 ღ</strong></p>
<p><strong>Would you like some orange juice?</strong></p>
<p>来杯橙汁怎么样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在英语中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有一些</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">令人容易混淆（迷惑）水果表达</p>
<p>0 2圣女果是什么意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圣女果也就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家常说的“小西红柿”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">英文可不是small tomato</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它的正确表达是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">↓↓↓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>cherry tomato</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201201/73bb0c4b3447404793a028befa008aa3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>0 3火龙果是什么意思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">火龙果可以说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">pitaya ['pɪtəjə]</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它还有另外一个名字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>dragon fruit</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果里面的果肉是红色的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们可以说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>red dragon fruit</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201201/5ecbc08ee5d941d49b1e5e80e7dc0db4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原来水果的英语表达有这么多奥秘</p>